room_title: Escape room "The Agency" by Escape the Room Chicago in Chicago
review: Need one in Memphis. This place was awesome and well thought out. All the employees were super nice and helpful

room_title: Escape room "The Agency" by Escape the Room Chicago in Chicago
review: My family got together during a visit from out of state relatives and we did the Agency escape room. We had a lot of fun. It was a little too dark for us older ones but the teenagers were able to help us out. The staff were very nice and helpful. We managed to escape with a few minutes to spare so we were very pleased! We all definitely want to do another one.

room_title: Escape room "The Agency" by Escape the Room Chicago in Chicago
review: Great time with friends. Very nice place. I would recommend everyone go to the Oakbrook location and try one of the rooms.
